---
// Démo GitLab CI/CD : pipeline visualization — identique FR/EN
---
<p class="text-slate-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">.gitlab-ci.yml</p>
<div class="space-y-1.5">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>
    <span class="text-green-400 font-bold">build</span>
    <span class="text-slate-600 ml-auto">12s</span>
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>
    <span class="text-green-400 font-bold">test</span>
    <span class="text-slate-500 text-[10px] ml-2">coverage: 87%</span>
    <span class="text-slate-600 ml-auto">34s</span>
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>
    <span class="text-green-400 font-bold">documentation</span>
    <span class="text-slate-600 ml-auto">8s</span>
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>
    <span class="text-green-400 font-bold">release</span>
    <span class="text-slate-500 text-[10px] ml-2">v1.2.0</span>
    <span class="text-slate-600 ml-auto">5s</span>
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0"></span>
    <span class="text-green-400 font-bold">deploy</span>
    <span class="text-slate-500 text-[10px] ml-2">→ AWS EC2</span>
    <span class="text-slate-600 ml-auto">22s</span>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="mt-2 pt-3 border-t border-slate-800 text-slate-500 text-[10px]">
  Pipeline #47 · passed · triggered by push to <span class="text-yellow-400">main</span>
</div>
